Hello CQAS,                    Is your ship the one we see at Chongqing right now, QAS Chongqing? If so, we have 3,000MT of barium nitrate from Marseilles to Dalian, which we urgently need to schedule. Please do quote us a rate, and could you send us your terms and conditions by return?                    Kind regards,                    Stephen
