Subject: List of documents                     To reserve this vessel, pls find below attached the required documents:

1. Bill of Lading, 1 set;
2. P&I Club certificate, 1 set;
3. A1 Tanker certificate, 1 set;
4. Charter Party, 1 set;
5. Release of any attachments or liabilities and other documents as may be requested by the mortgagee. A mortgagee's consent may be required.
6. Master's account, 1 set;
7. Draft survey, 1 set;
8. Stability Certificate, 1 set;
9. Safety equipment certificates, 1 set;
10. MCA Authorization to use electronic chart display and information system (ECDIS), 1 set;
11. Oil record book, 1 set;
12. Third-party damage report and certificates, 1 set;
13. All maritime papers
